# Assessing Projects

#### In the previous level, you learned how you might use **check-in** and **assessment** levels to guide your instruction. 

#### The Programming with Music Lab curriculum also provides **project rubrics** to help you summatively assessment students' work on projects.

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px auto;">
  <img 
    src="https://images.code.org/885618e5046b154d6142f792c9683612-image-1751492570512.42.45 PM.png" 
    alt="The Lesson 5: Mini-Project Walk up Songs lesson plan" 
